  <brief_title>Human Epidermal Growth Factor Receptor 2 (HER2) Advanced Gastric Epidemiology Study in Korea</brief_title>
  <official_title>HER2 Advanced Gastric Epidemiology Study in Korea: An Assessment of HER2 Status in Tumor Tissue Samples of Gastric and Gastro-esophageal (GE) Junction Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hoffmann-La Roche</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Hoffmann-La Roche</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to gather epidemiological data in Korea on HER2 incidence in gastric
      and gastroesophageal junction cancer as assessed by local laboratories in a real-life
      setting. No investigational products will be provided or evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
